We are disturbed in the transmission of sovereignty to Europe - but it is the whole of Europe, which is slowly losing its sovereignty and with it each of its peoples.
The management of the European project of democratic sovereignty must be urgently returned.
For only together will Europeans be able to reduce the burden of their debts, to get rid of the government of the markets and to prepare the future by investing.
